00:09:23.863 --> 00:09:25.998
Hezbollah is one of them, the Houthis.

00:09:25.998 --> 00:09:27.333
They they have other militias

00:09:27.333 --> 00:09:28.968
and forces throughout the Middle East.

00:09:28.968 --> 00:09:30.970
But Hezbollah is the largest

00:09:30.970 --> 00:09:32.138
and the most capable

00:09:32.138 --> 00:09:34.240
of all of those proxy forces. Right.

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:36.142
So the concern about escalation

00:09:36.142 --> 00:09:37.310
is the most acute

00:09:37.310 --> 00:09:38.945
when we're talking about Hezbollah.

00:09:38.945 --> 00:09:39.579
Right.

00:09:39.579 --> 00:09:41.981
The thing that could lead to a larger

00:09:41.981 --> 00:09:42.782
