And Hezbollah has vowed that

00:09:55.962 --> 00:09:57.463
depending on the Israeli response,

00:09:57.463 --> 00:09:58.297
they wouldn't go to war

00:09:58.297 --> 00:09:59.365
with Israel alone.

00:09:59.365 --> 00:10:00.032
To your point,

00:10:00.032 --> 00:10:02.001
